Description (en): Gavun Wud is a community-driven Polkadot memecoin inspired by Dr. Gavin Wood, co-founder of Ethereum and Polkadot. It aims to unite Web3 enthusiasts and onboard new users into the Polkadot ecosystem through engaging meme art, NFTs, AI agent and gaming experiences.
Description (zh): Gavun Wud是由社区驱动的Polkadot memecoin,灵感来自Dr。Ethereum和Polkadot的共同创始人Gavin Wood。它旨在通过吸引模因艺术,NFT,AI代理和游戏体验,将Web3爱好者和新用户加入Polkadot生态系统。
